797","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/qura4--m5dOziq_qauctpo5wlsDKeVCbqFcE8IGD7533ZsrDxXXti54FtRA4bkGS1KkqCHD2PA=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@NicoNico-79797","is_favorited":true,"_time_text":"1 year ago","timestamp":1745884800,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzvbbVuY-TdDBeEbjd4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"La morte di questo Maestro è stato uno degli eventi più tristi della mia esistenza assieme alla fine perenne di Top Gear/ Grand Tour.","like_count":2,"author_id":"UCT_uZBQ7vtAF-OykgMmjuTQ","author":"@UrbanVoodoo","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_kBPHQGGEevbzxk1BEYSkxlIyKqW2wHLSdUUSO1TTe1piZv=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@UrbanVoodoo","is_favorited":true,"_time_text":"1 year ago","timestamp":1745884800,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzemDFk4GQakfcN_P94AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"wow  che ricordi...robazza a via cavour ,ci presi nel '77 una gherson imitazione stratocaster e un fbt da 50 w","like_count":1,"author_id":"UCWUWYHq6eCM59E3OiZKFuMA","author":"@platini450","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_k0VE36NqEfnDiJiYD5maBH51OdZ8qHI8z0MhCqfE0=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@platini450","is_favorited":true,"_time_text":"1 year ago (edited)","timestamp":1745884800,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugz0nJ-rA6wSUU-hItV4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Mitico Franco, quanti ricordi.","like_count":5,"author_id":"UCtPQQZtYz8y0Kl-qDckAXtg","author":"@JGRStudios","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_nZsmYvlEXtPmPlE_UyZi5H9IpFe3aBkmE9jNfLBfdVWz16=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@JGRStudios","is_favorited":true,"_time_text":"1 year ago","timestamp":1745884800,"is_pinned":false},{"id